xxl.core.spatial.geometries.cursors

Class SpatialJoin<F,R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • xxl.core.cursors.SecureDecoratorCursor<E>
      • xxl.core.cursors.filters.Filter<R>
        • xxl.core.spatial.geometries.cursors.SpatialJoin<F,R>
  • Type Parameters:
    F - The return type of the filterstep (usually an array of KPEs).
    R - The return type of the refinement-step (usually an array of Geometry2D- objects).
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterator<R>, Cursor<R>

    public class SpatialJoin<F,R>
extends Filter<R>
    An abstract multi-step Spatial Join: the join takes an input cursor of possible join- candidates identified by a filterstep and returns those candidates which satisfy the given refinement predicate.
